g.text: SOP-1006-01-AI: AI-IRB Engagement and Ethical Review Sequence
Identify AI aspects needing IRB oversight
Determine if full submission or consult
LIAISON advises next steps for formal IRB
Collect technical/data details for Ethical Review Dossier
Request preliminary check of dossier completeness
Submit final Ethical Review Dossier to IRB
(If needed) Clarify conditions or regulatory constraints
Confirm updated design meets IRB demands
Provide logs or metrics for ongoing IRB reviews
Provide updates to IRB, if required
Prepare final IRB summary and lessons learned
